Author: eattillithurts
Text: i am so sad, but its hard to help you through the PC, maybe its possible to open up about some issues with someone you trust? maybe find a counsellor to which you only go one time? it helps a lot, well, a lot of people not everyone, to talk about it with a person. or you can join peach? there was a peach thread a few days ago  i wish you good luck, and you should update us here how you feel later? stay strong. as long as you try there is a chance of getting better and having luck
